trans-unit.source: Represents a collection that contains the key field of each record in a data source.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling som inneholder nøkkelfelt for hver oppføring i en datakilde.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan arves.

trans-unit.source: The DataKeyCollection class represents a collection of the key fields in the data source.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DataKeyCollection representerer en samling av nøkkelfeltene som er i datakilden.

trans-unit.source: The key field of each record in the data source is stored in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Nøkkelfeltet for hver oppføring i datakilden lagres i denne samlingen.

trans-unit.source: This allows you to store the key field with a data listing control without displaying it in the control.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør at du kan lagre nøkkelfeltet der opplisting kontrollen uten å vise den i kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: This collection is automatically filled with the values from the field specified by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BaseDataList.DataKeyField%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Denne samlingen automatisk fylt med verdiene fra feltet som er angitt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BaseDataList.DataKeyField%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BaseDataList.DataKeyField%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: This collection does not allow you to manually add or remove items from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Denne samlingen tillater ikke at du manuelt legge til eller fjern elementene i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The key field is commonly used in a handler for an event, such as `ItemCommand` or `DeleteCommand`, as part of an update query string to revise a specific record in the data source.
trans-unit.target: Nøkkelfeltet ofte brukes i et behandlingsprogram for en hendelse som `ItemCommand` eller `DeleteCommand`, som en del av en oppdatering spørringsstreng å endre en bestemt post i datakilden.

trans-unit.source: The key field helps the update query string identify the appropriate record to modify.
trans-unit.target: Nøkkelfeltet hjelper oppdateringen spørringsstrengen identifisere riktig post til å endre.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection.Count%2A> property to determine the number of items in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection.Count%2A>til å fastslå hvor mange elementer i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: To programmatically retrieve a key field from a DataKeyCollection, use one of following methods: - Use the indexer to get a single key field from the collection, using array notation.
trans-unit.target: For å hente et nøkkelfelt programmatisk fra en DataKeyCollection, bruker du én av følgende metoder:-Bruk indekserer til å hente et enkelt nøkkelfelt fra samlingen matrise notasjon.

trans-unit.source: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection.CopyTo%2A> method to copy the contents of the collection to a <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object, which can then be used to get items from the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection.CopyTo%2A>metode for å kopiere innholdet i samlingen til en <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>objektet, som kan brukes til å hente elementer fra samlingen.</xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection.CopyTo%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection.GetEnumerator%2A> method to create a <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> implemented object, which can then be used to get items from the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>metode for å opprette en <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>implementert objektet, som kan brukes til å hente elementer fra samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to create and initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne konstruktøren til å opprette og starte en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.ArrayList"></xref> that contains key fields from the data source.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Collections.ArrayList"> </xref> som inneholder nøkkelfelt fra datakilden.

trans-unit.source: Copies all the items from the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"></xref> to the specified <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object, starting at the specified index in the <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object.
trans-unit.target: Kopierer alle elementer fra de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"> </xref> til den angitte <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> objektet, med Start fra den angitte indeksen i den <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Use this method to copy the contents of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection> into the specified <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object, starting at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne metoden til å kopiere innholdet i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection>i den angitte <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>objektet, med Start fra den angitte indeksen.</xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The `array` parameter must be a zero-based <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den `array` -parameteren må være en nullbasert <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>objektet.</xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A zero-based <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object that receives the copied items from the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En nullbasert <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> objektet som skal motta kopierte elementer fra de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The first position in the specified <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object to receive the copied contents.
trans-unit.target: Den første posisjonen i den angitte <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> objekt for å motta kopierte innholdet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of items in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter antallet elementer i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Use the Count property to determine the number of items in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk Count-egenskapen til å finne ut hvor mange elementer i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: This property is commonly used when iterating through the collection to determine the upper bound.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen brukes vanligvis under gjentakelse samlingen til å finne den øvre grensen.

trans-unit.source: The number of items in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Antall elementer i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Creates a <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> implemented object that contains all key fields in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> implementert objekt som inneholder alle nøkkelfelt i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Use this method to create a <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> implemented object that can be iterated through to get each item in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne metoden til å opprette en <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>implementert objektet som kan være iterated til å hente hvert element i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to get the item currently pointed to in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>til å hente elementet som er angitt i samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move to the next item in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden til å flytte til neste element i samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move the enumerator to its initial position.
trans-unit.target: Bruk den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden til å flytte enumeratoren til den opprinnelige plasseringen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > After you create a <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> implemented object or use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move the enumerator to the first item in the collection, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Når du har opprettet en <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>implementert objekt, eller bruk den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden til å flytte enumeratoren til det første elementet i samlingen du må kalle den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the item represented by the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: Ellers elementet som representerer den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen er ikke definert.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> implemented object that contains all key fields in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> implementert objekt som inneholder alle nøkkelfelt i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether items in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"></xref> can be modified.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om elementer i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"> </xref> kan endres.

trans-unit.source: This property always returns `false` to indicate that the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection> can be written to in all cases.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen returnerer alltid `false` å angi at den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection>kan skrives til i alle tilfellene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> for all cases.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>for alle tilfellene.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"></xref> is synchronized (thread-safe).
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"> </xref> synkroniseres (sikker).

trans-unit.source: This property is derived from the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection?displayProperty=fullName> interface and is overridden to always return `false` to indicate that the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection> is not thread-safe.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er avledet av den <xref:System.Collections.ICollection?displayProperty=fullName>grensesnittet og overstyres for å returnere alltid `false` å angi at den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection>er ikke sikker.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection> </xref:System.Collections.ICollection?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For more information on the IsSynchronized property, see the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.IsSynchronized%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection?displayProperty=fullName> interface.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om egenskapen IsSynchronized, se den <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.IsSynchronized%2A?displayProperty=fullName>-egenskapen til det <xref:System.Collections.ICollection?displayProperty=fullName>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.ICollection.IsSynchronized%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> for all cases.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>for alle tilfellene.

trans-unit.source: Gets the key field at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter nøkkelfeltet i den angitte indeksen i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Use this indexer to get the key field from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection> at the specified index, using array notation.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne indekserer til å hente nøkkelfeltet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection>i den angitte indeksen matrise notasjon.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection>

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the key field to retrieve from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den nullbaserte indeksen for nøkkelfeltet til å hente fra samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The key field at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Nøkkelfeltet i den angitte indeksen i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the object used to synchronize access to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter objektet brukes til å synkronisere tilgang til den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The object returned in this implementation is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection> object itself.
trans-unit.target: Objektet returnerte i denne implementeringen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection>selve objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataKeyCollection>

trans-unit.source: For more information on the SyncRoot property, see the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection?displayProperty=fullName> interface.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om egenskapen SyncRoot, se den <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A?displayProperty=fullName>-egenskapen til det <xref:System.Collections.ICollection?displayProperty=fullName>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Object?displayProperty=fullName> that can be used to synchronize access to the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object?displayProperty=fullName> som kan brukes til å synkronisere tilgang til samlingen.
